{
  "texts": [
    "Even partial control may attenuate the risk for high calorie intake (McKay et al., 2023).",
    "For instance, the health score of food can be awarded to a delivery portal, and the rating system can be employed.",
    "Consumers concerned about health were likely to order the food type when given a good label and health score (Grummon et al., 2023).",
    "Education interventions can enhance the dietary care of consumers and help with a healthy diet.",
    "Public health organizations can use food delivery apps to remind people of unhealthy consumption and provide health tips."
  ]
}